WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.199
I was praying and the Lord showed me, saying, 'I need you to pray for Italy.

00:00:05.199 --> 00:00:07.563
' I asked, 'What's going on with Italy, Lord?

00:00:07.563 --> 00:00:26.199
' He showed me—I had that open vision again—a massive volcano that's about to happen.

00:00:29.306 --> 00:00:44.120
I saw a coastline on the water where there's a massive volcano.

00:00:44.120 --> 00:01:04.839
He told me this is going to happen and there will be signs right before a massive explosion.

00:01:16.293 --> 00:01:25.740
I saw this thing explode huge, and He kept having me pray over the ocean.

00:01:25.740 --> 00:01:33.944
There's something about the water around Italy.

00:01:33.944 --> 00:01:55.239
I believe the volcano was right there, because Pompeii is right here and there's a massive volcano up here.

00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:29.780
When I was looking over in the spirit realm, I thought it was in this area, but I believe it's probably further out.

00:02:37.983 --> 00:02:46.660
I started looking at where the massive volcanoes in the water are in Italy.

00:02:46.660 --> 00:03:08.240
If you zoom out, I'll show you; one of the largest is way down here.

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:39.639
Whenever I saw this massive volcano going off out of the water, it caused a massive tsunami wave.

00:03:39.639 --> 00:04:24.600
From the earthquake and this massive volcano, it was like a humongous nuclear bomb went off—it went up out of the water and caused a massive wave.

00:04:26.250 --> 00:04:39.450
The water rushed all over this area, causing a lot of devastation.

00:04:39.450 --> 00:04:52.509
The Lord is showing me it came up out of the water and caused all the air traffic around that area to be completely shut down.

00:04:52.509 --> 00:05:10.589
The Lord showed me it would cost hundreds of thousands of deaths.

00:05:16.577 --> 00:05:49.840
There will be signs, maybe even on the news in Italy, about rumblings around that area, earthquakes, or tremors to warn that something big is going to happen.

00:05:49.840 --> 00:06:01.714
Do not ignore this; it is very serious.

00:06:01.714 --> 00:06:19.035
If you start having a lot of tremors and you start seeing smoke, take heed.

00:06:19.035 --> 00:06:26.319
Be forewarned; I'm trying to tell you.

00:06:36.208 --> 00:06:43.545
I was just praying in the spirit, worshiping, and all of a sudden I was shot up.

00:06:46.300 --> 00:07:03.186
I was looking over Italy, and it looked so small because I was so high up.

00:07:11.414 --> 00:07:21.470
I was looking down and all of a sudden I could see a black blanket over the water.

00:07:21.470 --> 00:07:40.240
It was a very thick cloud, as black as molasses, very dark.

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:57.560
I could see the black clouds going through all the houses like a smog.

00:08:10.420 --> 00:08:13.908
I could see the rooftops of the homes and the lights on inside.

00:08:16.096 --> 00:08:43.720
The Lord pointed my attention to a massive circle, a humongous portal over Italy near where the volcano was by Pompeii.

00:08:43.720 --> 00:08:53.577
Angels were coming out of this massive portal.

00:08:53.577 --> 00:09:05.766
It was alive, swirling with clouds, and opening up.

00:09:09.160 --> 00:09:35.000
All of a sudden, thousands of angels started coming out of this massive portal like soldiers, lined up and descending.

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:52.560
Through the portal, clouds were coming out—humongous, beautiful pink, fluffy, blue, and purple.

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:03.200
I believe it was Heaven.

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:13.524
These angels were descending onto the Earth.

00:10:13.524 --> 00:10:37.209
When they reached the atmosphere, they started to spread out like ants, moving at the speed of light on a mission.

00:10:37.209 --> 00:10:46.915
They all had beautiful robes and gowns on.

00:10:46.915 --> 00:10:51.679
It was amazing.

00:10:51.679 --> 00:10:56.462
I'm just sitting here in this chair praying in the spirit, soaking it all in.

00:10:57.075 --> 00:11:23.220
I asked the Lord what that black smog was, and He showed me there is a lot of trafficking and corruption in Italy.

00:11:23.220 --> 00:11:42.319
Those angels were going to homes and waving their hands, telling people to leave, warning them.

00:11:42.319 --> 00:11:52.045
You could sense an urgency on their faces.

00:11:52.045 --> 00:11:59.200
All of a sudden, the angels stopped.

00:12:01.240 --> 00:12:14.017
I could feel the intercessory prayers from the saints interceding for Italy in the spirit.

00:12:14.017 --> 00:12:30.806
You could feel the blanket of prayer above the atmosphere.

00:12:30.806 --> 00:13:04.017
All of a sudden, all the angels froze and turned their bodies to look back up to the massive swirling light of the portal.

00:13:04.017 --> 00:13:14.787
They started shooting back up into that portal.

00:13:14.787 --> 00:13:29.680
Then the Lord took me to another part of the vision.

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:41.920
He said, 'I want you to focus on the canary.

00:13:41.920 --> 00:13:56.650
' What is the meaning of a canary in a coal mine?

00:13:56.650 --> 00:13:59.657
Study this out.

00:13:59.657 --> 00:14:10.874
I saw a yellow canary in a cage.

00:14:20.256 --> 00:14:26.624
There was gas like a smog coming up out of the ground.

00:14:36.247 --> 00:14:38.680
The canary was swinging in its cage in the spirit realm.

00:14:38.680 --> 00:15:03.960
It was chirping, but then I looked down at the mist coming up out of the ground.

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:26.120
When I looked back up, the canary was at the bottom of the cage, lifeless.

00:15:26.120 --> 00:16:02.697
This gas coming up out of the ground in Italy—I don't know if it was from the volcano, but I saw hundreds of thousands of people go home.

00:16:02.697 --> 00:16:09.920
A massive wave was coming.

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:21.594
The Lord said to pay attention to the water.

00:16:21.594 --> 00:16:36.971
I saw earthquakes in the water, and He kept pointing me to that in the spirit realm.

00:16:36.971 --> 00:16:58.089
In my spirit eyes, I could see the water in the gulf area, the gulf right there by Pompeii.

00:16:58.374 --> 00:17:25.748
For three weeks now, the Lord has spoken to me about the electric grid in America, telling me to pray over the electric grid.

00:17:25.748 --> 00:17:26.875
This is serious.

00:17:26.875 --> 00:17:36.000
I saw a cyberattack or a false flag.

00:17:42.630 --> 00:17:44.760
Power went out in New York and major cities.

00:17:44.760 --> 00:18:02.191
He warned me that I need to pray about this more intently because of what is being planned.

00:18:09.996 --> 00:18:23.938
I saw that when the electric grid went down, it had the opportunity to be down for over three weeks.

00:18:24.808 --> 00:18:31.783
I saw a calendar with the days going by.

00:18:31.783 --> 00:18:56.124
He showed me a year ago to invest in a generator with three fuel types—propane, gas, and natural gas—and solar power.

00:18:56.739 --> 00:19:12.565
I don't want to preach fear, but I get these intense warnings from the Spirit of God.

00:19:13.054 --> 00:19:37.480
For instance, I was praying over an ice storm once and He told me about Texas being without power.

00:19:50.630 --> 00:19:52.370
I kept seeing no heat and a poisoning of the water.

00:19:52.370 --> 00:20:11.520
About three years ago, a major arctic front made everything really cold in Texas.

00:20:23.700 --> 00:20:38.760
The grid shut down, pipes burst, and they put out a warning not to drink the water because it had E.

00:20:38.760 --> 00:20:40.657
coli.

00:20:40.657 --> 00:21:03.120
Before that happened, the Lord warned me to tell friends in Texas they needed cases of water.

00:21:03.120 --> 00:21:23.084
I bought water too because what I was seeing in the spirit was very alarming.

00:21:23.084 --> 00:21:42.933
Even if it doesn't always affect everybody, I want to be quick to obey.

00:21:45.919 --> 00:21:55.159
I saw New York, a major city with big buildings.

00:21:55.159 --> 00:22:02.555
Pray about the power grid with me.

00:22:09.644 --> 00:22:41.386
I don't want to be a Debbie Downer and coming on here and going wacky all the time, but these are the three things: the canary, Italy, and the electric grid.

00:22:41.386 --> 00:22:45.060
Let's pray.

00:22:50.605 --> 00:22:50.980
Father, I thank You.

00:22:52.949 --> 00:23:05.559
We lift up Italy, the volcano, and the earthquakes.

00:23:21.239 --> 00:23:21.599
You warned us that perilous times would come.

00:23:21.599 --> 00:23:46.040
Shake us and show us what we're supposed to do for our families so we hear You before danger comes.

00:23:46.040 --> 00:24:00.120
Let us not be led by emotion, but by the Holy Ghost.

00:24:20.280 --> 00:24:32.687
I pray for every person watching this video, that they would learn to yield themselves to the Spirit of God.

00:24:32.687 --> 00:24:50.297
We call for clarity and supernatural giftings to see into the spirit realm.

00:24:50.297 --> 00:25:03.070
We take authority over cyberattacks and false flag events.

00:25:13.220 --> 00:25:17.303
We plead the blood of Jesus over our power grid.

00:25:19.360 --> 00:25:28.680
We say we will have power.

00:25:28.680 --> 00:25:54.145
Give wisdom to Homeland Security and the computer people to protect us from foreign adversaries.

00:25:54.145 --> 00:25:59.350
Expose all wicked plots.

00:25:59.350 --> 00:26:09.110
I pray over finances for a hundredfold return.

00:26:09.110 --> 00:26:23.629
I speak blessing over homes—raises, bonuses, and checks in the mail.

00:26:23.629 --> 00:26:33.500
Every need is met and every debt is cancelled.

00:26:33.500 --> 00:26:43.199
I pray over their health and bodies.

00:26:51.225 --> 00:26:55.017
We take authority over sickness, cancer, and addictions.

00:26:56.251 --> 00:27:07.905
We call for rain to break drought—the former rain, the latter rain, and even the spiritual rain of the Holy Ghost rain over this nation.

00:27:07.905 --> 00:27:16.617
Bring an outpouring of Your Spirit.

00:27:18.626 --> 00:27:34.830
We pray for the leaders, from Joe Biden down, that they would have a fear of the Lord to make godly decisions.

00:27:45.547 --> 00:27:51.239
In Your presence is fullness of joy.

00:27:51.679 --> 00:27:58.343
We will not fear.

00:27:58.343 --> 00:28:00.788
Amen.
